summary: Adds some oculor justu eyes and others from the anime/manga Naruto.
descriptionHtml:
Adds some standalone oculor justu eyes and others from the anime/manga Naruto. Right now there are Byakugan, Eternal Mangekyo Sharingan, Itachi\'s Eternal Mangekyo Sharingan, Kakashi\'s Mangekyo Sharingan, Nine-Tails Sage Mode, Rinnegan, Sagemode, Sasuke Eternal Mangekyo Sharingan, 1-3 Stages of Sharingan, and Orochimaru. 13 eyes total for each race.

Enter showracemenu in the console to change eyes.

ALL RACES NOW SUPPORTED

And before you say something, I know that the single eye sharingan doesn\'t work at certain angles. (only female nords until I find out why)

Feel free to suggest any eyes that you feel I should add.
author: AntiiMatter
